title: Stamp Proper Foods
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Juice bar, Mexican, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. An all gluten-free casual cafe offers a wide variety of labeled vegan items, from buckwheat banana pancakes to chilaquiles, chickpea mash sandwiches and avocado toast. Also has four or five vegan baked goods daily, along with vegan gelato. Also has juices and vegan shakes.
